track_notes: As the road trip to the departure is a bit long drive, it is nice to clim a neighboor summit as Tournairet or Brec dUtelle. The walk is a nice path in the forest until the last part where you leave the path to clim 150m slope to summit. The landscape is very nice.
This is an easy way to reach this summit from la Vallee de la Vesubie
The second summit is not very far, so it is good idea to walk few rocks and activate.
I found a parking (2 cars here), the walk is fine until you climb the last edge, where you must look for your way, thinking of the way down. Nice place for radio and panorama
track_title: Nearly the same track in winter
